overview: 'If you liked ROCK' EM SOCK' EM HOCKEY, your gonna love ROCK' EM SOCK' EM HOCKEY VOLUME II; great hits, goals, bloopers and much, much more. We even have a few Coach's Corner highlights, and wait till you hear 'Grapejam'.  This is hockey the way I like it - Full of fun, Fire and Action!'
tagline: Highlights from the 1989-1990 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry.
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Volume 2
